Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.21,0:04:06.30,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,政治上仍处于不安定的状态
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.52,0:04:12.85,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,玛斯德·拉弗玛迪被什么人绑架了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.03,0:04:15.73,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么会发生这种事…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.36,0:04:20.50,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,保守派大概会认为是我们改革派做的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.01,0:04:24.07,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不  这有可能也是事实
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.66,0:04:28.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,联合国的支援似乎只能带来灾难呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.68,0:04:31.66,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,议会已经同意太阳光发电了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.10,0:04:35.11,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但并不是所有的国民都赞同吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.88,0:04:39.52,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,议会已经决定出动治安部队了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.79,0:04:45.29,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,激进保守派采取行动也只是时间的问题了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.83,0:04:50.45,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,而且万一  玛斯德·拉弗玛迪死亡的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.67,0:04:52.55,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,别说了  这种不吉利的话
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.17,0:04:57.37,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,仔细想想吧  即使是为了避免最恶劣的事态
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.86,0:05:01.45,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,最恶劣的…事态
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.61,0:05:06.76,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,内战…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.66,0:05:15.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,忘记神的教诲的人  接受神罚吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.72,0:05:23.81,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,无法和普特利麦奥斯取得联系
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.34,0:05:27.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,回到拉格朗日4的话  还需要一些时间
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.20,0:05:33.32,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,阿扎提斯坦如果发生内战的话  只能以目前战力来应对了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.83,0:05:39.95,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是我  你那边的状况如何
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.63,0:05:44.21,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,到处都有小规模游行  但是似乎没什么大事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.56,0:05:46.46,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,请立刻转移到国外避难
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.82,0:05:48.02,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我们会留在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.45,0:05:50.34,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,留下来  为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.73,0:05:53.17,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,想见证这个国家的前进方向
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.64,0:05:58.93,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,而且  想亲眼看看你们会采取怎样的行动
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.65,0:06:04.39,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,调查追溯到200年前
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.72,0:06:08.42,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,获得博士称号的人中  失踪和下落不明者
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.75,0:06:10.36,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,一共是138名
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.14,0:06:13.43,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,能查查最近的失踪者吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.79,0:06:14.58,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.89,0:06:15.45,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,特报
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.81,0:06:17.43,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,阿扎提斯坦的宗教指导者
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.68,0:06:20.65,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,玛斯德·拉弗玛迪好像被武装势力绑架了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.05,0:06:22.21,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,阿扎提斯坦吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.69,0:06:25.61,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,对联合国技术支援的特派采访记者应该还在
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.92,0:06:27.50,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,联系他去进行报道
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.72,0:06:28.15,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.65,0:06:30.95,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,会出现吗  Celestial Being
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.45,0:06:32.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,大概会吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.77,0:06:38.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀  看起来很好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.71,0:06:41.67,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,也不用特地送过来啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.27,0:06:44.87,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,跟我说的一样吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.11,0:06:46.42,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,妈妈对这些东西很没抵抗力的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.62,0:06:47.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就只有一张批萨饼而已
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.34,0:06:49.15,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.33,0:06:49.82,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.99,0:06:50.99,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这身衣服是？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.26,0:06:54.19,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  我在这家店打工
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.42,0:06:57.78,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,妈妈  沙慈他双亲很早就过世了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.07,0:07:00.48,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,现在和他姐姐相依为命
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.03,0:07:03.54,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀  双亲都…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.33,0:07:06.48,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,于是才这样特意打工
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.09,0:07:09.21,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,很了不起啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.55,0:07:10.62,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不  这个…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.97,0:07:12.39,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,妈妈很容易流泪的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.68,0:07:13.74,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,容易得也太过头了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.44,0:07:16.07,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你是叫沙慈吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.40,0:07:17.36,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.99,0:07:20.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,仔细看的话长得还是相当不错的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.92,0:07:22.27,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,诶  是么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.20,0:07:24.13,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,很像啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.46,0:07:26.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  和什么很像…？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.38,0:07:29.01,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,跟我丈夫很像
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.28,0:07:31.33,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,才不像呢  而且爸爸还活着！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.45,0:07:41.37,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,拉撒  玛斯德·拉弗玛迪
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.90,0:07:45.98,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是么  终于下定决心了么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.50,0:07:51.10,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是的  我决定继位为本国的公主
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.60,0:07:56.56,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,即使是作为新生阿扎提斯坦的象征  摆设般的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.22,0:08:01.02,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,也要尽我自己的全力
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.46,0:08:02.82,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,所以  拉撒…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.18,0:08:06.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那么  我就选择持反对意见
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.28,0:08:09.12,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这…这是为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.24,0:08:12.78,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,仔细听好  玛丽娜公主
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.59,0:08:16.13,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,即使国家得到新生
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.54,0:08:19.14,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,在这片土地上生活的历史仍在
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.47,0:08:22.44,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,家族仍在  神的教诲仍在
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.84,0:08:24.89,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不喜欢变化的人仍然很多
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.18,0:08:27.12,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我也是其中之一
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.01,0:08:32.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,即使是为了让反对你的人不再起纷争
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.82,0:08:36.25,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,能接受他们思想的存在也是必要的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.82,0:08:40.61,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,拉撒
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.20,0:08:44.37,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我所做的一切是错误的吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.78,0:08:51.04,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,席琳  议会听取了我的意见了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.57,0:08:52.51,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,双方的让步…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.65,0:08:54.10,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不是这种状况
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.71,0:09:03.27,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,保守派不理会议会  改革派则要接受联合私下商谈的军事支援
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.55,0:09:06.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这样做的话只会刺激保守派人士啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.07,0:09:09.05,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,而且  为什么联合会…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.68,0:09:12.11,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,为了保护这个国家  利益什么的…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.54,0:09:14.54,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,有的吧  肯定
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.22,0:09:19.13,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,中尉  似乎能遇到久违的Gundam了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.42,0:09:20.82,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不是这样的话可就伤脑筋了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.05,0:09:23.62,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是  居然向阿扎提斯坦出兵…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.94,0:09:27.11,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这是军方高层向议会施加压力的结果啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.45,0:09:29.95,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不能落后于人革联啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.73,0:09:39.05,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,内战开始之前  两位请在机内待机
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.68,0:09:42.08,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然很窄  但是已经准备好了房间了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.55,0:09:44.54,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不错呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.85,0:09:45.94,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,酒店  酒店
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.37,0:09:47.14,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那么  那边呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.71,0:09:50.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,要平息阿扎提斯坦的内部纷争
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.18,0:09:53.84,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就得保护被绑架的玛斯德·拉弗玛迪氏
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.16,0:09:56.76,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,并对全国民通告其平安
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.29,0:10:00.64,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,话是这么说  但这个国家的国民讨厌异国文化
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.09,0:10:02.71,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,会有怎样的结果
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.08,0:10:03.97,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我也出发吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.54,0:10:05.34,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你来？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.76,0:10:07.67,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我是出身于阿扎提斯坦的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.89,0:10:08.53,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.92,0:10:09.73,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这个国家的？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.16,0:10:15.20,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,刹那  不要因为是故乡的危机就感情用事哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.60,0:10:16.58,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.83,0:10:24.44,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,绑架玛斯德·拉弗玛迪的组织不是改革派的可能性很高
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.70,0:10:26.01,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这是吠陀的推测
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.34,0:10:28.23,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,保守派的内部争斗吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.47,0:10:30.37,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,也有可能是第三势力
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.04,0:10:36.08,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这个国家里有制造纷争的人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.61,0:10:47.87,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那种事…还打算继续吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.92,0:11:00.65,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,大哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.59,0:11:02.68,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,要买水吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.33,0:11:04.73,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不  还够用
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.10,0:11:06.95,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不会是第一次来这里吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.37,0:11:09.11,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我一直在周游世界
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.28,0:11:12.53,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那个  族长和我说过
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.86,0:11:16.07,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这个世界上有非常高的塔  能去宇宙
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.19,0:11:16.81,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.14,0:11:19.64,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  是真的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.02,0:11:21.45,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,难不成你去过
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.84,0:11:22.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,算是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.85,0:11:24.15,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,太棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.46,0:11:27.87,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,玛丽娜小姐说过  我们有一天也能去宇宙
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.23,0:11:28.94,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,玛丽娜？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.16,0:11:29.99,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不认识吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.31,0:11:34.30,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,看  那边的海报里的就是玛丽娜·伊斯迈尔小姐哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.99,0:11:41.50,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,玛丽娜·伊斯迈尔
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.71,0:11:42.98,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  在做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.64,0:11:45.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你是克鲁吉斯人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.62,0:11:46.77,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,看长相就知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.09,0:11:48.03,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,爷爷…？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.38,0:11:51.97,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这里不是你待的地方  快离开这里
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.71,0:12:02.68,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不会吧  居然想让联合支援
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.35,0:12:07.07,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,他们好像不知道部队里也有保守派
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.10,0:12:18.37,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,一定得想方设法从这里逃出去
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.90,0:12:23.12,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这样下去  这个国家会再次陷入动乱时代
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.48,0:12:31.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那么  这回神会选择哪边呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.44,0:12:35.44,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不过  不管选哪个都会是战争啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.62,0:12:49.22,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.97,0:12:57.52,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,要让扰乱这片土地的背叛神的家伙们领教神的愤怒！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.67,0:13:00.66,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,D地点陷入交战
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.06,0:13:02.57,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,目标果然是天线吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.99,0:13:04.51,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,上吧  Flag Fighter
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.79,0:13:05.37,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.43,0:13:12.48,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,中尉  是在自相残杀呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.78,0:13:13.45,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.16,0:13:15.66,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哪边才是叛徒
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.32,0:13:18.04,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,雷达…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.07,0:13:23.70,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.72,0:13:27.77,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这种粒子束光线…是Gundam吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.93,0:13:31.11,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,全弹命中  全弹命中
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.68,0:13:33.29,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,在这待机看来是对的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.53,0:13:35.10,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这招如何  小哥
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.07,0:13:37.54,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.76,0:13:38.62,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,导弹
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.52,0:13:43.84,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,数量太多了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.71,0:13:56.75,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,太阳光天线被破坏了？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.19,0:13:58.27,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,到底是谁…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.99,0:14:04.98,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好像有激进保守派的人混入了进行警卫的MS机师中
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.35,0:14:06.23,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么会…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.49,0:14:11.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,简直是预测到玛斯德·拉弗玛迪被劫持了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.47,0:14:17.71,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,有计划的反抗  怎么会…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.37,0:14:25.36,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,霍华德  达利尔  追击进行导弹攻击的敌人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.79,0:14:27.11,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,Gundam交给我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.44,0:14:27.95,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.24,0:14:29.62,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,Gundam交给你了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.55,0:14:38.52,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,喂喂  联合的任务难道不是防卫阿扎提斯坦吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.96,0:14:40.72,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我们果然是目标吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.11,0:14:43.07,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,狙击！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.12,0:14:52.50,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是被人称作的  格拉哈姆特别版
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.62,0:14:54.90,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哈罗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.13,0:14:56.24,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,明白  明白
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.49,0:14:59.51,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不会有第二次了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.09,0:15:03.05,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我居然会打偏？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.29,0:15:04.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这个机师怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.77,0:15:07.30,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,让我告诉你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.33,0:15:11.07,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我可是格拉哈姆·艾卡
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.92,0:15:14.29,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,居然用脚踢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.82,0:15:22.68,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,居然让我用剑
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.93,0:15:24.98,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,滴水不漏的防御啊  Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.74,0:15:27.46,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.42,0:15:29.01,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.72,0:15:33.54,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,承受住了？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.12,0:15:37.75,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,居然把我的Flag…！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.40,0:15:39.81,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这么缠人  真不一般
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.27,0:15:42.37,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哈罗  停止GN粒子的散布
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.63,0:15:44.08,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,将全部发动机转向火炮运作
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.39,0:15:45.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,明白  明白
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.19,0:15:47.63,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,明明只是Flag而已
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.27,0:15:48.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.76,0:15:52.65,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,阿扎提斯坦军泽伊尔基地  发现MS行动
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.05,0:15:54.42,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,目的地好像是王宫
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.81,0:15:56.66,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,紧急通知
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.79,0:15:56.67,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,请立即前往
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.87,0:16:01.38,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,估计其它基地也会采取什么行动
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.51,0:16:02.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,阿扎提斯坦军吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.93,0:16:06.92,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,MS部队擅自从泽伊尔基地出发了？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.94,0:16:09.72,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,难道是…政变？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.23,0:16:14.10,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,MS总共有5台  直接朝着这里来了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.34,0:16:15.86,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,公主殿下  快去掩体避难
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.05,0:16:16.52,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.62,0:16:17.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,请快
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.93,0:16:21.86,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我们是神的长矛  我们要报复
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.75,0:16:26.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,要让忘记神的教诲的家伙们知道神的愤怒
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.87,0:16:30.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,驱逐将脚伸向订有契约的土地的异教徒
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.84,0:16:37.29,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不用去避难吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.94,0:16:40.52,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,李本兹  你也看好了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.38,0:16:43.20,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,名为Gundam的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.62,0:16:47.95,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,刹那·F·清英
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.69,0:16:50.66,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,Exia  驱逐目标
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.23,0:16:57.31,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,可是政变啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.70,0:17:00.53,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,准备怎么办  Flag的机师啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.93,0:17:04.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好不容易才能遇上Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.05,0:17:08.56,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但毕竟怎么说  我也是今非昔比的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.74,0:17:14.03,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,霍华德  达利尔  去防卫首都
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.29,0:17:14.87,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.27,0:17:16.51,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,发射导弹的家伙呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.98,0:17:20.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,似乎确认是MS  但由于特殊粒子的关系…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.92,0:17:23.08,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,还得考虑Gundam的能力啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.74,0:17:46.19,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那就是…Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.72,0:17:50.77,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,全靠力量  过于依赖Gundam的性能
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.89,0:17:54.90,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,机师是刹那·F·清英吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.31,0:17:58.90,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.37,0:18:01.87,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,卡兹纳基地的MS部队也出发了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.39,0:18:04.07,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,现在正在经过第七区域
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.38,0:18:04.98,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.44,0:18:07.20,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的  没完没了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.13,0:18:18.08,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.71,0:19:15.37,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,Exia
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.40,0:20:00.93,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,在联合国正予以技术支援的中东国家阿扎提斯坦王国
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.19,0:20:04.12,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,Celestial Being似乎进行了武力干预
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.20,0:20:07.23,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,阿扎提斯坦是哪里啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.42,0:20:09.48,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,记得应该是中东…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.57,0:20:10.76,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,别靠这么近啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.52,0:20:20.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,皇小姐  吠陀发来的紧急密码消息
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.40,0:20:24.50,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,在阿扎提斯坦发生政变？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.25,0:20:33.74,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,增援部队已经确保了整个首都圈的制空权
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.98,0:20:39.56,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,若过于信赖的话  就会招致这种悲剧吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.41,0:20:44.54,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶啊  真有一套啊  Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.02,0:20:47.16,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好戏明明才刚要开始的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.38,0:20:53.89,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,政变爆发
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.47,0:20:58.93,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,还允许了Celestial Being的干预
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.43,0:21:01.90,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,现在我们受到了联合部队的保护
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.23,0:21:04.20,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,政变也即将平息了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.53,0:21:05.34,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,请放心
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.14,0:21:11.37,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是  这点燃了国民内心里愤怒的火焰
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.28,0:21:16.38,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我所做的事情…将这个国家引向了战争…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.89,0:21:21.15,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,请保持坚定  玛丽娜·伊斯迈尔
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.02,0:21:24.37,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,还没结束  还没有
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.93,0:21:34.14,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真是惨象
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.73,0:21:36.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,发现Exia  发现Exia
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.35,0:21:43.26,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,刹那…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.45,0:22:00.65,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我…无法成为Gundam…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.36,0:23:38.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,信念被粉碎了的刹那面前  阿里·阿尔·沙谢斯出现了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.81,0:23:42.19,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,为了根除纷争  Exia重新站了起来
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.70,0:23:44.73,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,下集  「圣者回归」
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.29,0:23:47.61,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,刹那  成为Gundam
